lead_paragraph: Dallas Mavericks owner Mark Cuban declared that Oklahoma City's Russell Westbrook is "not a superstar" and then watched as the point guard eliminated the Mavs from the playoffs on Monday.

headline.print_headline: Westbrook Responds in Style to 'Not-Superstar' Jibe
